description.en:
"A community built and driven static protocol with reflective rewards, reliquidation pool, and an autonomous yield mechanism.

upShib frictionless farming reflects a 3% based tax fee from every single transaction a distributes it to wallet holders. The liquidity is also constantly increasing in token amounts as upShib distributes based fees from transactions to the liquidity pool."
